{"tid":1687172,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"希望大家可以唔好極大量瘋狂\"推\" 行動post","createTime":"2019-11-01T15:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T00:47:00.000Z","uid":163149,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"68f7840db9fba41cadc9f014d3bcc78ac9ce2d6f","tid":1687172,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:44:03.000Z","msg":"呢排成日有人話熱門睇唔到行動post, 又話好多廢post 上左熱門。<br />\n其實有幾點想大家思考下<br />\n<br />\n(1) 其實唔駛咁在意個post 係唔係熱門。 我自己上高登or連登都唔會淨係睇熱門，通常都係揀台再睇topic 爬文睇。<br />\n      不過可能今次運動多左人新上連登，我唔肯定佢地閱讀習慣，不過我地更宣揚<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好只睇熱門post</span>, 好過成日問點解點解呢個post 上唔到熱門。<br />\n<br />\n(2) 連登係討論區， 討論為主， 不是公告板。 有d 你認為係廢post 既點解會上熱門？ 當中可能因為有argue, 有討論，keep 住大家有回應， 一人一句就好快爆post. <br />\n<br />\n而點解所謂行動post 會沉或者上唔到熱門？ 因為開post 果下有野睇之外，之後都冇野可以討論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">［行動］V煞：永生難忘的11月5日。新模式行動 V is all of us終極整合！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1686681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1686681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n以呢個post 為例， 其實我想入去睇下大家有冇其他野討論， 但各位<span style=\"color: red;\">實在推得太密</span>啦， 一粒鐘百幾個推， 其實真係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會有心機再討論或者睇其他人既回覆</span>， 因為感覺就係1000 個回覆有900 個都係&quot;推&quot;. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實一個post 真係唔需要每分鐘都係度推，反而引發下大家討論或者思考更加好</span>, 而唔係單純係度推。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(3) <span style=\"color: red;\">Topic 要開得好</span>，唔瘋狂推post 但係要多d 人知內容要點做？ 要做既就係開個好d 既topic. <br />\n務求令到睇連登既人，就算時間唔多都可以碌幾頁得到資訊同埋睇自己想睇既topic. <br />\n<br />\n最好就避免開類似以下topic:<br />\n&quot;點解呢個post 上唔到熱門&quot;<br />\n&quot;唔想個活動完就入黎睇下&quot;<br />\n<br />\n其實呢d topic 就算長期係熱門都未必好吸引人睇， 當然我自己有時間會爬大部分post, 但其他人真係未必。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個post 都唔需要推啦， 有野就討論， 冇野都唔好格硬留推， 沉半粒鐘推一次我都已經覺得好密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加唔講其他post 每半分鐘就有人推， 咁樣只會扼殺討論。<br />\n<br />\n到時冇人想爬文睇回覆&gt; 大家知道回覆冇人睇但有野想發表又開新post&gt; 個個開新post 當回覆咁用發表意見 &gt; 成個討論區就資訊會好混亂"},{"pid":"22e7bd828488154a0a1e37cbe4c43fceeecb59c3","tid":1687172,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b89def6cebef7a5ebf16859449ac637e9e535bd2","tid":1687172,"uid":164435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:51:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得熱門可以有少少其他生活嘢囉<br />\n唔好見到唔關抗爭事就話拉<br />\n<br />\n始終有啲人唔係日日上連登<br />\n如果連登可以Keep到有啲生活嘢睇嘅話可能可以吸引佢哋多啲開App"},{"pid":"dae5a385842f897a6d82b51450a18f509f2d7265","tid":1687172,"uid":11254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"講得好呀 <br />\n班傻西開個post推上熱門就當做左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面全部留言都推推推 推乜鳩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8238edc7a8a8e9d82d38a6fd81a9470282ddc3","tid":1687172,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b89def6cebef7a5ebf16859449ac637e9e535bd2","tid":1687172,"uid":164435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:51:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得熱門可以有少少其他生活嘢囉<br />\n唔好見到唔關抗爭事就話拉<br />\n<br />\n始終有啲人唔係日日上連登<br />\n如果連登可以Keep到有啲生活嘢睇嘅話可能可以吸引佢哋多啲開App"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:54:27.000Z","msg":"時事台鍵國上腦囉 <br />\n明明呢到係一個討論區黎 <br />\n唔撚明點解熱門只可以有時事台d post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2aab44ac4d62f6bf1be1cf99b9fae6116c0062","tid":1687172,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b89def6cebef7a5ebf16859449ac637e9e535bd2","tid":1687172,"uid":164435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:51:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得熱門可以有少少其他生活嘢囉<br />\n唔好見到唔關抗爭事就話拉<br />\n<br />\n始終有啲人唔係日日上連登<br />\n如果連登可以Keep到有啲生活嘢睇嘅話可能可以吸引佢哋多啲開App"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:10:00.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該更重於教大家點係連登睇想睇既野<br />\n一般都係揀你想睇既範疇去果個台睇<br />\n<br />\n熱門我真係想睇下有咩八卦野先會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個連登咁多人， 一定咩topic 都有人討論， 未必要太在意熱門有咩post"},{"pid":"489b7092fb9fa5a10823e236a8115f271361a465","tid":1687172,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dae5a385842f897a6d82b51450a18f509f2d7265","tid":1687172,"uid":11254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"講得好呀 <br />\n班傻西開個post推上熱門就當做左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面全部留言都推推推 推乜鳩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"咁又唔好咁mean, 不過我反而覺得依家連登少左野睇姐<br />\n<br />\n因為大部分post 我都係入去望一望內文就走， 冇乜心機爬回覆"},{"pid":"0bd8beab04ae0fb0421178b15163e2e4e7cb6812","tid":1687172,"uid":288190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:14:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf8d712af01594788bd4a22df93d1d8c8c1d53e3","tid":1687172,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:19:31.000Z","msg":"準備出街"},{"pid":"aac48c82ef19b6db17b07c8561f96894fb4b47d5","tid":1687172,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"我都覺得多d討論會好過推，尤其是d行動post/狗狗暴行post"},{"pid":"52857a77ac654bbd9595c531baa78b2d6c3e0f31","tid":1687172,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ce2b060eefd039f4cb05b4a631f949bf0a1d1f","tid":1687172,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:43:34.000Z","msg":"講左好多次架啦 但班友唔會理"},{"pid":"476671246e6d82cf61b8903e7b914c1acaa7bf4a","tid":1687172,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"推到有中大手足見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[緊急] 唔想中大手足少個機會比人告暴動入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1715763\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1715763</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d7680d4e9faa62c7b9d90d250554030af0d5df3c","tid":1687172,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T00:21:18.000Z","msg":"5個月前既連登終於返黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698638\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698638</a><br />\n<br />\n連登一過區選又變撚晒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1759038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1759038</a><br />\n<br />\n我係要成個熱門都係時事台嘅post 吹?~"},{"pid":"3915650c8ed484027b8aa0c5304857240606cc44","tid":1687172,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T00:27:53.000Z","msg":"又好似有d道理，其實有啲po真係得#1有野睇，然後就全部得個推字，變相係推緊個標題，唔係推緊個po<br />\n如果唔介意剩係推topic，咁就麻煩大家改好啲個名，唔好做標題撚，唔係人人見到都會入去睇你入面打乜9"},{"pid":"d5314aa94c778b9f338bd0be7cb97797348b47b3","tid":1687172,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T00:30:04.000Z","msg":"惡性循環嚟 正如樓主呢個咁重要嘅post 冇人推係唔會有人見到"},{"pid":"c05d3ddef981cded833e4eb8180f71bfb7ebfca8","tid":1687172,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T00:44:18.000Z","msg":"所以行動post會唔會放另一個台好啲？<br />\n學你話齋 呢啲post冇乜討論 純資訊 好靜態<br />\n但唔推真係沉L曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11.29 行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1761123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1761123</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a78d98f377a7b0dec96aff38803d4d06d319e1c8","tid":1687172,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T00:47:00.000Z","msg":"其實過某正負數就自動熱門一段時間唔得咩？"}]}